name: Jinnix
content:
Jinnix was a male Nihil Storm serving in Pan Eyta's Tempest. Jinnix led a Storm of Eyta's Tempest that raided a shipment of glitterstim in the Abrion sector.
Jinnix once lived in a nest with a dronemate of his and a queen. The hueche raided their nest, and the drone mate failed to protect the queen. When they explained the reasons they couldn't protect the queen to Jinnix, he ripped off their head and ate their ganglia.
The Twi'lek colony planet Aaloth began exporting stim in the aftermath of a coup d'Ã©tat. An informer for Pan Eyta within the Hutt Cartel informed the Tempest Runner of a shipment along the Roon Way shortly after a previous shipment. Jinnix's Storm engaged a cargo vessel piloted by RL-18 and crewed by the Twi'lek Lourna Dee. He was killed by Lourna with his own spike.
Jinnix appeared in flashbacks in the 2021 audio drama The High Republic: Tempest Runner, written by Cavan Scott and performed by a full voice cast.
